  "body": "### What was wrong?\r\nWhen working in fork mode, the gas limit is handled identically to a normal development environment.  This can cause issues when doing a dry-run prior to running on the actual mainnet, because an account may not have enough gas to cover [block gas limit] * [gas price].\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed?\r\nHandle gas costs in fork-mode more in line with production.",
